l? Not only is it soteriological, it constitutes what I know to be the very essence of classical soteriology: interventive miracle that saves my life; my welfare is secured permanently; I am told \"you deserved it\"; I am as it were taken up to Paradise; I see God (Valis); an angelic voice guides me; I am told it is my \"tutelary spirit\" + that I \"have been adopted\"; it is mystagogue; + it tells of a savior to come - + finally I am told that in fact the savior is here - not \"born\" but \"transplanted + is alive\". This is indubitably the very engine of utter soteriology itself, utter + absolute; it reveals the apocalypsis, the Parousia + the Millenial Kingdom; it speaks of a vast war against evil in which evil did not merely lose, it was seen + it was \"brought to justice\". So this soteriology is set in context within the classical Judo-Xtian end times: it is, then, an historical drama played out on the world stage. Now, it is interesting that this congruence to -adherence to- soteriology can be viewed as a scale indicating veracity; it never strays from its topic: the savior + salvation. While my mind veers from topic to topic, it stays constant. folder 57 - 005 folder 57 - 005 Q-9 It wants to talk about soteriology + so it does, whatever I may wish to know. + it acts as Soter, + began that way back when I was in eleventh grade physics. By pure chance I happened to read the E.B. micro-entry \"soul\". Since I postulate (1) endless horizontal tracking (i.e. again + again, with the memory erased each time); + (2) my being lifted up (vertically) by \"the pulley\" (i.e. extricated) due to a moral act on my part (operating in conjunction with an extraordinary intellectual act, the meta-abstraction) then according to this article I am down to 3 + no more systems: Orphics, Hindus + Buddhists. Okay. The moral act springing me (i.e. causing my salvation) is of course Judo-Xtian - but the endless horizontal tracking is not. Conversely, the endless horizontal tracking is 